      { question: "Where's the best sunset at Lake Tahoe?", answer: "Sand Harbor on the east shore offers the best sunsets with the mountains as backdrop. Emerald Bay lookouts are also spectacular. The west shore gets the best light at sunrise if you're an early riser." }
